  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reuniting pets affected by Hurricane Harvey with their families Best Friends Animal Society&apos;s priority.  On September 11, in partnership with Harris County Public Health and Houston Pet Set, we opened the Pet Reunion Pavilion at NRG Arena in Houston, where we&apos;re caring for nearly 500 displaced cats and dogs. The Pet Reunion Pavilion will be open until November and we expect at least 1,500 animals to pass through our care and we will keep arranging for transport of hundreds more.</narrative>
  </description>
